Set Up the Supervisor Workspace

Set up Omni Supervisor, your supervisors' workspace. First, enable it. Then add Omni Supervisor to an app where your supervisors work.

This feature is available with these telephony models:

SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH AMAZON CONNECT
SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH PARTNER TELEPHONY FROM AMAZON CONNECT
SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH PARTNER TELEPHONY

After you're done configuring your contact center, you can begin using it. When you're ready, consider customizing your contact center to meet your specific business needs. All customization tasks are optional.

Enable Omni Supervisor
Add Omni Supervisor to an App
title: Setting Up the Supervisor Workspace in Service Cloud
